text: Oh my god! This is almost genius. This is beat for beat a late 90's/early 20's family film. I mean they got the entire formula down to a T! The A list actors, the jokes, the music, the god awful animal CG, the obviously disinterested animal manipulation! That trailer narration literally sounds like it was pulled directly from a movie 15 years ago! There's literally nothing new! No new twist of any kind. This isn't just "like a late 90's/2000's cheesy family movie", this IS every cheesy 90's/2000s family film! This seriously looks like a missing fake trailer from Tropic Thunder or something. They HAD to know what they were doing. This had to have been a joke. There is absolutely no way anyone involved in this film intended for this to be a real movie, meant for 2016 audiences! Just that horribly looped shot of the cat doing pull ups is more than enough evidence!
